        "TileImage": "$($repository 7b019d42-3157-46f4-9f0a-e9bfa31caca8).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\r\rYour target is Fan Ren, former member of the Chinese militia group Hi-Zan. Ren betrayed his former confederates to the government in exchange for expulsion of his robbery crimes, and is now in hiding as a laundromat owner. \r\rRecently taken to accompanying Fan Ren is S. Wen, a small-time heroin dealer who spends his summers hunting endagered animals in Africa.\r\rOur client would like them both eliminated with a box cutter. They did not specify why, but it seems personal.",
